name: StellarBrink - Open-World, RPG, Mining, Crafting, Space Game
blurb: Think... Open-World, Isometric, Role-Playing, Sci-Fi, Crafting, Mining, Building, and Battling in space with custom Starship Interiors.

rewards.reward: ----Copper Member Reward ---- Just your way of saying "Keep Up The Good Work!" ---- You get: ---< A great big Thank You from the StellarBrink Team > ---- < 25 in-game credits > ---- < Copper Member Status in the StellarBrink Credits >

Iron Member Reward - This is the Early Bird Special Reward, so grab it quick before it's gone. You get: a great big Thank You from the StellarBrink Team, a copy of the Final Game upon its release, access to the Open Beta, 100 in-game credits, and Iron Member Status in the StellarBrink Credits.

Silver Member Reward - This is the Get The Game Reward You get: a great big Thank You from the StellarBrink Team, a copy of the Final Game upon its release, access to the Open Beta, 125 in-game credits, and Silver Member Status in the StellarBrink Credits.

Zinc Member Reward - This is the Early Bird Get The Game and Shadow Faction Reward You get: access to the Shadow Faction, a great big Thank You from the StellarBrink Team, a copy of the Final Game upon its release, access to the Open Beta, 150 in-game credits, and Zinc Member Status in the StellarBrink Credits.

Zirconium Member Reward - This is the Get The Game and Shadow Faction Reward You get: access to the Shadow Faction, a great big Thank You from the StellarBrink Team, a copy of the Final Game upon its release, access to the Open Beta, 150 in-game credits, and Zirconium Member Status in the StellarBrink Credits.

Chromium Member Reward - This is the Early Bird Get The Game And Poster Reward. Gives you a cool 16"x12" poster. You get: 16"x12" poster, access to the Shadow Faction,a great big Thank You from the StellarBrink Team, a copy of the Final Game upon its release, access to the Open Beta, 150 in-game credits, and Chromium Member Status in the StellarBrink Credits.

Silicon Member Reward - This is the Get The Game And Poster Reward. Gives you a cool 16"x12" poster. You get: 16"x12" poster, access to the Shadow Faction, a great big Thank You from the StellarBrink Team, a copy of the Final Game upon its release, access to the Open Beta, 150 in-game credits, and Silicon Member Status in the StellarBrink Credits.

Gold Member Reward - This is the Get The Game And Mouse Pad Reward. You get: a StellarBrink Pirate Faction Gel Mouse Pad, access to the Shadow Faction, a great big Thank You from the StellarBrink Team, a copy of the Final Game upon its release, access to the Open Beta, 175 in-game credits, and Gold Member Status in the StellarBrink Credits.

Platinum Member Reward - \r\nThis is the Get The Game And T-Shirt Reward. Gives you a choice between a Pirate T-Shirt or a Alpha T-Shirt. You get: choice of StellarBrink Pirate Faction T-Shirt or Alpha Faction T-Shirt, access to the Shadow Faction, a great big Thank You from the StellarBrink Team, a copy of the Final Game upon its release, access to the Open Beta, 250 in-game credits, and Platinum Member Status in the StellarBrink Credits.
